</P>
<P>
   MEAT-RECALLS (Undated) _ Contamination of hot dogs and cold cuts
by a sometimes deadly bacterium _ a germ that is little known by
the public _ has led to an extraordinary series of recalls in
recent months, as well as increased government action to detect the
problem sooner and prevent it. By Marian Burros.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 2 p.m. ET in `a' category.)
