</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-IOC-DATA-$ADV14-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    IOC BY THE NUMBERS: BIRTH OF A REVENUE-GENERATING MACHINE
