<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-13 23:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9624 &Cx1f; tic-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SMALLPLANE-AZR &LR;      03-13 1349
